title: Some Samsung Galaxy S7 Versions with Exynos M1 Could Have Only 3GB of RAM
text: According to the most recent hearsay, Samsung is apparently striving to ready the Samsung Galaxy S7 ahead of schedule (the company usually unveils its next-gen S flagship at MWC in early March), just like it did with the Galaxy Note5.
